    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "self-care... that sounds like a joke. how do you \"self-care\" your way out of being a social pariah? the people i used to lead, the clients, even my own family... they look at me like i'm a disease. there is no \"rebuilding\" from this. you can't rebuild a person when the foundation is just completely rotten. it's just dead. everything is just dead.",
